snippet.title: JOHNNY DEPP v Amber Heard (The Sun) | Johnny Depp WITNESS Statement (1 of 3) Full Readthrough
snippet.description:
This video Johnny Depp v Amber Heard is a full readthrough of Johnny Depps third witness statement from the UK trial. The first was not available but a source has sent it too me. Thank you

This is the fifth of multiple videos to be released every 2-3 days, each covering another witness statement from the Johnny Depp v Amber Heard (The Sun) trial in the UK.

Big thanks to Les for doing the voice over for each female witness.
